title: NFL ATL: Week 2 Recap
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Week 2 Recap
description:
A room full of heroes, Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling breakdown everything you need to know about all of the Week 2 action. Get caught up on all the analysis and key takeaways from each game. Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL.
